{
    "openapi": "3.0.0",
    "info": {
        "title": "Seni Kolor API",
        "description": "API untuk aplikasi Seni Kolor dengan berbagai metode autentikasi: JWT Bearer Token, Basic Auth, dan API Key.\n *                  \n *                  ## Cara Testing di Swagger UI:\n *                  \n *                  ### 1. JWT Authentication (Bearer Token)\n *                  - Klik endpoint `/api/login` untuk mendapatkan token\n *                  - Input credentials: admin@example.com/password atau customer@example.com/password\n *                  - Copy `access_token` dari response\n *                  - Klik tombol 'Authorize' (ðŸ”’) di kanan atas\n *                  - Di bagian 'bearerAuth', masukkan: Bearer {your_token}\n *                  - Klik 'Authorize' â†’ Sekarang bisa test semua endpoint JWT\n *                  \n *                  ### 2. Basic Authentication\n *                  - Klik tombol 'Authorize' (ðŸ”’) di kanan atas\n *                  - Di bagian 'basicAuth', masukkan:\n *                    * Username: admin@example.com atau customer@example.com\n *                    * Password: password\n *                  - Klik 'Authorize' â†’ Sekarang bisa test endpoint Basic Auth (Read Only)\n *                  \n *                  ### 3. API Key Authentication\n *                  - Klik tombol 'Authorize' (ðŸ”’) di kanan atas\n *                  - Di bagian 'apiKeyAuth', masukkan: HQldYrXmCAojpQfYzRxJXqbx9vg9EG4d\n *                  - Klik 'Authorize' â†’ Sekarang bisa test endpoint `/api/secure-data`\n *                  \n *                  ## Role Permission:\n *                  - **Admin**: Bisa CRUD semua endpoint JWT + Read endpoint Basic Auth\n *                  - **Customer**: Hanya bisa Read endpoint JWT & Basic Auth\n *                  - **API Key**: Hanya bisa akses endpoint `/api/secure-data`",
        "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    "servers": [
        {
            "url": "http://localhost:8000",
            "description": "Laravel Development Server"
        }
    ],
    "paths": {
        "/api/login": {
            "post": {
                "tags": [
                    "JWT Auth"
                ],
                "summary": "Login user",
                "operationId": "222b2625838e3c57e017987f73598fda",
                "requestBody": {
                    "required": true,
                    "content": {
                        "application/json": {
                            "schema": {
                                "required": [
                                    "email",
                                    "password"
                                ],
                                "properties": {
                                    "email": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "example": "admin@example.com"
                                    },
                                    "password": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "example": "password"
                                    }
                                },
                                "type": "object"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                "responses": {
                    "200": {
                        "description": "Login success",
                        "content": {
                            "application/json": {
                                "schema": {
                                    "properties": {
                                        "access_token": {
                                            "type": "string"
                                        },
                                        "token_type": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "bearer"
                                        },
                                        "expires_in": {
                                            "type": "integer",
                                            "example": 3600
                                        },
                                        "scope": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "admin"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "type": "object"
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "401": {
                        "description": "Unauthorized"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "/api/me": {
            "get": {
